{"tid":45773,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"細數學生搵錢方法","createTime":"2016-12-19T07:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T12:50:40.000Z","uid":67741,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d6f8d6c97c9dbabe98aa1b59bfc5b29b069bb2","tid":45773,"uid":67741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"大學五件事，其中一項就係做part time.你知啦 上左大學咩都係錢 re-u 上莊 玩ocamp等。而本人就靠part time 學費自己交。咁作為學生究竟可以點搵錢好呢？以下我會介紹下（排名分先後）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.網賺<br />\n網賺絕對係合法！小弟由year 1開始玩 玩到依家個個月起碼都過千，玩一年已經可以交半年學費。或者你會諗得千幾蚊咁少，但係坐係度蹺住對腳日日做十幾分鐘就有WO 都咪話唔正。<br />\n講番其實網賺主要係做下任務同survey、一份平均有個幾美金。佢仲有個下線系統可以抽佣，不過詳情等你地自己發掘啦。<br />\n<br />\n1.clixsense(始創於2007年,最老牌且非常有信譽的一個綜合網上賺錢網站)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.clixsense.com/?10270792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.clixsense.com%2F%3F10270792&d=R%2F%2BmfF0kYNTsCQBSFggLuWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=1e89803b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.clixsense.com/?10270792</a><br />\n我覺得依個真係幾好 夠穩定同唔會呃你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有neobux 不過我覺得麻麻地。<br />\n同埋網賺真係要堅持同有恆心，初頭你可能會覺得賺得好慢，但係當你第一次見到户口入左錢果陣，真係好似賺左咁，<br />\n同埋當你搵得越多下線就好穩得同收入都會唔錯<br />\n<br />\n2.私補<br />\n記住唔好俾人壓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，大學生$200/HR是常識吧。好處就係舒服同彈性，唔好就係可能老西咁遠你都要去。<br />\n<br />\n3.馬會投注<br />\n好處：算高人工，有得坐，超HEA<br />\n壞處：工時有限制，唔俾你返得多，成日俾客嘈<br />\n<br />\n4.夜間保安<br />\n好處： 可以去到600一日，超HEA成晚睇片<br />\n壞處：要捱夜，學生有D難就時間，唔可以怕黑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他果D飲食業真係唔好啦，做到成隻狗咁，做Sale又要企成日人工又低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f5aded7decc7ef71a6961c059678660a0475b4","tid":45773,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:54:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你"},{"pid":"09499d41c5c0cb372b54f3a7d2609634edf45247","tid":45773,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8506ef5a90d20d6f058d083bedf15630ea50f8b4","tid":45773,"uid":34310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"打手味濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685b57df3f632fe01cc2bbc99709e70a2c95e48f","tid":45773,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"已檢舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e273182289fecdcc06310291f9d5260a3cf209","tid":45773,"uid":60115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:57:12.000Z","msg":"ptgf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同毒撚出一次街，唔駛扑野都有幾千蚊收入"},{"pid":"914404446e5bbde5a27bbbb8ef7a5f0a35d9dde4","tid":45773,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:58:05.000Z","msg":"做左AMWAY同埋SELL 保險之後<br />\n我覺得我既人生正面同充實好多<br />\n多謝老闆/朋友們比呢個機會我學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e63693de7dc1292b54e57342e5d31f26d0e1e4","tid":45773,"uid":45173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"本身樓主諗住上黎賣下廣告<br />\n但驚比人屌，所以加多2,3個方法<br />\n扮撚曬真心推薦咁<br />\n第一點可以寫幾百字<br />\n下面果d就兩行講完<br />\n犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor